text: Dinet Oosting (born 15 May 1991) is a Dutch softball player from Veendam. In 2021 she played her 400th match in the Dutch national league. She is the nineteenth ever Dutch women who have reached this. She was decorated for this by the national federation. She is member of the Netherlands women's national softball team. With the national team she became European champion at the 2022 Women's Softball European Championship where she was one of the important players in the final. Dinet now studies criminology at the Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam.
